        <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-d60f20e487a04931834cbf4ad6964414" textAlignment="1">
          <bounds x="2064" y="48" width="185" height="97"/>
          <content>User workstation can either access frontend via Webseal or directly connect to API endpoints on backend via APIGW if has sufficient rights</content>
        </child>
        <child xsi:type="archimate:Note" id="id-c3ee4898ad73446fb7f478d430b89c43" textAlignment="1">
          <bounds x="2064" y="144" width="185" height="109"/>
          <content>Multiple servers communicate with backend API endpoints. Communication is mostly towards OT, but there are few cases when OT needs to call API of servers on HPC.
</content>
        </child>
